sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant User as User
  participant Cmd as enhancePrompt command
  participant Clip as Clipboard utility
  participant Scrub as scrubText()
  participant MM as ModelManager
  participant Worker as LLM Worker

  User->>Cmd: Trigger keybinding
  Cmd->>Clip: Capture selection via synthetic copy
  Clip-->>Cmd: raw text + previous clipboard state
  Cmd->>Scrub: Redact sensitive entities to typed placeholders
  Scrub-->>Cmd: scrubbed text + entity metadata

  alt LLM enabled and model available
    Cmd->>MM: load() if not already ready
    MM->>Worker: load { modelId, cacheDir } (IPC)
    Worker-->>MM: ready
    Cmd->>MM: enhance(scrubbedText, systemPrompt, maxNewTokens)
    MM->>Worker: generate { id, system, user, maxNewTokens } (IPC)
    Worker-->>MM: result { id, text }
    MM-->>Cmd: enhanced text
  else Scrub only (LLM disabled or unavailable)
    Cmd-->>Cmd: use scrubbed text as final output
  end

  Cmd->>Clip: Paste replacement into selection + restore clipboard
  Cmd-->>User: Selection replaced with sanitized or enhanced text
